3 Method
3.1 Data
3.1.1 The Defense Logistics Agency
The Defense Logistics Agency provided information about all acquisitions from the 1033 Program (Bowden, 2015). Once collapsed and cleaned, there are 4282 state-month observations across 54 states from January 1991 through September of 2015, including Virgin Islands, Guam, District of Columbia, and Puerto Rico. All purchases for Federal agencies were removed from analysis.
